OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,FA national blue plaque has been
OL,7,Funveiled in Stoke-on-Tent to honour
OL,8,Fone of the most influential pottery
OL,9,Fdesigners of the 20th century
OL,11,FFamous for her colourful creations,
OL,12,Fmade history by being the first female
OL,13,Fart director in the potteries.
OL,15,FNow her services to pottery will be
OL,16,Fimmortalised with a blue plaque which
OL,17,Fhas been erected at her former home in
OL,18,Fthe town.
