OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,FShelia Jeffries' (former Cliff)
OL,7,Fgrandad is the cousin of Clarice Cliff
OL,8,Fand she was at the unveiling.
OL,10,FSheila said: "It's is such an honour
OL,11,Fand privilege to be here today.
OL,13,F"Clarice was such an amazing artist
OL,14,Fand her legacy is so revered in the
OL,15,Fcity and by us, the family.
OL,17,F"So to see that plaque today it feels
OL,18,Fsurreal, but it's so blissful, we
OL,19,Freally really are thrilled to bits.
