OL,6,FSheila says she can remember talking
OL,7,Fabout Clarice as a young girl about 10
OL,8,For 11, because her grandad and Clarice
OL,9,Fwere cousins.
OL,11,FShe said: "I was often there when
OL,12,Fgrandma and grandad were talking about
OL,13,FClarice, how she was related to us,
OL,14,Fhow proud were we and loved how well
OL,15,Fshe was doing.
OL,17,F"I've grown up with it really.
