OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,F"We've always known that Clarice is
OL,7,Fsomeone special in our lives, an
OL,8,Fabsolute pioneer, mega talented, we
OL,9,Fabsolutely love her to bits and this
OL,10,Fis just a great tonic.
OL,12,F"What a role model we've got. The
OL,13,Fpottery industry has been in the Cliff
OL,14,FDNA for years, because most of the
OL,15,Ffamily worked at the pottery industry
OL,16,Fin some way or the other.
OL,18,F"My grandad worked worked on Royal
OL,19,FDaltons, he was a master potter.
