OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,F"Lots of the ladies went into the
OL,7,Fpottery industry either making or
OL,8,Fdecorating and it's just lovely to
OL,9,Fhave Clarice as a role model for
OL,10,Fgenerations. She did it and so can
OL,11,Fthey."
OL,13,FThe plaque was unveiled in Snow Hill,
OL,14,Fin the city's Shelton district.
OL,16,FClarice Cliff purchased the property
OL,17,Fas her first independent home and
OL,18,Flived there at the height of her
OL,19,Fpottery fame.
