OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,FWill Farmer, director Fieldings
OL,7,FAuctioneers Ltd, said: "When we look
OL,8,Fat Stoke-on-Trent, Clarice Cliff has
OL,9,Fbe one of the most iconic and
OL,10,Frecognisable legacies that this region
OL,11,Fhas created.
OL,13,F"I mean she is a classic rags to
OL,14,Friches story. She was a young girl,
OL,15,Fborn in Tunstall, who basically ended
OL,16,Fup becoming director of two potteries
OL,17,Fin Stoke-on-Trent.
