OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,F"And all that started through
OL,7,Fdetermination, sheer will and an
OL,8,Fabsolute vision for what she wanted to
OL,9,Fcreate and do.
OL,11,F"When we look at Clarice's work, the
OL,12,Fbig difference for her compared to her
OL,13,Fcompetitors at the time, many of them
OL,14,Fwere still looking backwards in terms
OL,15,Fof inspiration.
OL,17,F"Clarice was looking forwards. She was
OL,18,Fcompletely aware of the wider world,
OL,19,Fof the wider art movements.
