OL,3,CBlue plaque honour for 'revered'
OL,4,Cpottery designer Clarice Cliff
OL,6,F"Everything that was happening across
OL,7,Fin Paris, in Europe and she wanted to
OL,8,Fbring huge colour and joy to what she
OL,9,Fsaid the house life of the day.
OL,11,F"And she did this through her pots,
OL,12,Fwhether they were vases, teapots for
OL,13,Fthe tableware or plates, or plaques
OL,14,Fwhatever it was, but it was all about
OL,15,Fthe sheer joy of colour, pattern and
OL,16,Fvibrance."
